    "deployment_instructions": {
      "value": "部署完成！请按以下步骤操作：\n\n1. SSH到实例：\n   ssh -i ~/.ssh/Knowhere-Test.pem ubuntu@18.144.15.15\n\n2. 配置DNS（在Squarespace中）：\n   apitest.knowhereto.ai -\u003e 18.144.15.15\n   test.knowhereto.ai -\u003e 18.144.15.15\n\n3. 运行首次配置：\n   cd /opt/knowhere/deploy/aws-ec2/scripts\n   sudo ./provision-instance.sh\n\n4. 部署应用：\n   sudo ./deploy-app.sh\n\n5. 访问应用：\n   API: http://apitest.knowhereto.ai\n   Web: http://test.knowhereto.ai\n",
      "type": "string"
    },
